flowchart TD
    EXPR["Filter Expression\n'tcp port 80'"] --> PARSE[Parse Expression]
    PARSE --> AST[Abstract Syntax Tree]
    AST --> COMPILE[Compile to Bytecode]
    COMPILE --> OPT[Optimize]
    OPT --> BPF[BPF Program]
    BPF --> KERNEL[Install in Kernel]

    subgraph "Filter Execution"
        PKT[Incoming Packet] --> EXEC[Execute BPF Program]
        EXEC --> ACCEPT{Accept?}
        ACCEPT -->|Yes| USER[Copy to Userspace]
        ACCEPT -->|No| DROP[Discard]
    end
